description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=0/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=1/3. Play five different modes: Battle, Challenge, Marathon, Practice, and Party - with up to 8 players (4 human + 4 computer). Pairs of blocks fall faster and faster - have you got what it takes to win?
